B) Embedded Multimedia elements.

Save everything in one folder:
multimedia-webpage
│
├── index.html
├── image.jpg
├── audio.mp3
└── video.mp4
Index.html
Code:-
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Embedded Multimedia</title>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Embedded Multimedia Webpage</h1>

    <hr>

    <!-- Image -->
    <h2>Image Example</h2>
    <img src="image.jpg" width="300" height="200" alt="Sample Image">

    <hr>

    <!-- Audio -->
    <h2>Audio Example</h2>
    <audio controls>
        <source src="audio.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
        Your browser does not support audio.
    </audio>

    <hr>

    <!-- Video -->
    <h2>Video Example</h2>
    <video width="400" controls>
        <source src="video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        Your browser does not support video.
    </video>

    <hr>

    <!-- YouTube Video -->
    <h2>Embedded YouTube Video</h2>
    <iframe width="420" height="250"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dQw4w9WgXcQ">
    </iframe>

</body>
</html>

